HEADWORD: Turfing
<hw>Turf"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or process of providing or
covering with turf.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>Turfing iron</b></col>, <col><b>Turfing
spade</b></col></mcol>, <cd>an implement for cutting, and paring off,
turf.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

